data.description: This country home features a split floor plan. As you walk in through the door, you are in the formal living room and dining room. Off to your right is the galley kitchen. Walk through the kitchen to get to the Master bedroom and ensuite. Next to the bedroom is the laundry room. From the front door, to your left is the 2nd bedroom, just past the formal living room is a bathroom and the 3rd bedroom. Keep walking forward from the front door is the 2nd living room which will take you to the fully fenced back yard.
